# Ninja Agents

AI agents for engineering teams. Each agent is self-contained under `agents/`. Full workflow specs live in `.claude/agents/{name}.md`.

## Workflows

Invoke by name (`@weekly-team-update`) or describe what you need. Each rule in `.cursor/rules/` points to its full spec.

## Key Rules

- GitLab queries MUST include `scope: "all"` or results may be empty
- Only `resolution = "Done"` counts as a completed Jira deliverable
- CSV fields with commas must be double-quoted; report links use markdown hyperlinks
- Never commit tokens or secrets — env vars only (`GITHUB_PAT`, `GITLAB_PAT`)

## Full Context

See [../../AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for conventions, patterns, and review guidelines. See [../../CONTRIBUTING.md](../../CONTRIBUTING.md) for contribution workflow. See `agents/_template/README.md` for new agent structure.
